1
00:00:08,141 --> 00:00:09,342
Why are you still here?

2
00:00:09,642 --> 00:00:11,044
To laugh at me?

3
00:00:11,544 --> 00:00:12,778
Yeah...

4
00:00:12,779 --> 00:00:14,246
I totally overestimated myself,

5
00:00:14,247 --> 00:00:15,815
and just went along with it.

6
00:00:16,449 --> 00:00:17,617
That's not what I meant.

7
00:00:18,318 --> 00:00:19,452
With the last-minute change,

8
00:00:20,120 --> 00:00:21,520
I was just worried you'd struggle.

9
00:00:21,521 --> 00:00:22,222
Struggle?

10
00:00:22,223 --> 00:00:23,757
Isn't that exactly what you wanted?

11
00:00:24,090 --> 00:00:25,324
To get rid of Ko Shasha

12
00:00:25,325 --> 00:00:26,159
and keep me here instead?

13
00:00:26,159 --> 00:00:26,993
We did the audition,

14
00:00:26,993 --> 00:00:27,993
only for you to say

15
00:00:28,395 --> 00:00:29,462
I'm too inexperienced?

16
00:00:30,263 --> 00:00:31,798
You and your manager are playing me.

17
00:00:34,467 --> 00:00:36,302
Excuse me, let me through.

18
00:00:36,636 --> 00:00:39,139
Good luck finding a
partner to compete with.

19
00:00:48,681 --> 00:00:50,750
Are you kidding me?

20
00:00:51,217 --> 00:00:52,317
Black&amp;White CP?

21
00:00:52,318 --> 00:00:53,920
Why even bother with a fan club?

22
00:00:54,550 --> 00:00:55,899
[A fan expressing their displeasure at this
currently not-real pairing for some normal reason]

23
00:00:55,923 --> 00:00:58,425
I'm clearly not good enough.
I'm not on your level.

24
00:00:59,559 --> 00:01:01,361
Alright, stop looking at that.

25
00:01:02,362 --> 00:01:03,897
I'm just asking you one thing:

26
00:01:04,597 --> 00:01:06,265
Keep your emotions in check,

27
00:01:06,266 --> 00:01:08,133
and watch your facial expressions.

28
00:01:08,134 --> 00:01:09,301
Got it?

29
00:01:09,302 --> 00:01:10,837
Try to be composed like Hei Yan.

30
00:01:11,638 --> 00:01:13,739
Well, he's a good actor.

31
00:01:13,740 --> 00:01:15,407
Your own artist is being insulted,

32
00:01:15,408 --> 00:01:16,743
and you're taking his side?

33
00:01:18,829 --> 00:01:20,756
[Another fan, this one being complimentary to
the pair despite Bai Xing's contrary conmment]

34
00:01:20,780 --> 00:01:21,614
Who is this "eyesonyou" anyway?

35
00:01:21,615 --> 00:01:24,384
Why do they keep
picking fights with me?

36
00:01:25,819 --> 00:01:26,419
Alright, that's enough.

37
00:01:26,419 --> 00:01:27,419
Let's get out of here.

38
00:01:27,687 --> 00:01:28,687
Hey,

39
00:01:29,522 --> 00:01:30,882
you forgot to return the necklace.

40
00:01:35,595 --> 00:01:36,596
Do it yourself.

41
00:01:38,932 --> 00:01:40,300
Get in the car.

42
00:01:43,136 --> 00:01:44,737
Do that again and I'll hit you.

43
00:01:52,645 --> 00:01:53,980
What was that all about?

44
00:01:54,414 --> 00:01:56,649
From Ko Shasha to the audition...

45
00:01:56,883 --> 00:01:57,784
If I didn't know better,

46
00:01:57,784 --> 00:01:58,618
I'd think you and Bai Xing

47
00:01:58,619 --> 00:01:59,819
were at the same agency.

48
00:02:00,220 --> 00:02:00,987
Ko Shasha's attitude

49
00:02:00,988 --> 00:02:02,554
couldn't be any worse.

50
00:02:02,555 --> 00:02:03,789
Bai Xing might be green,

51
00:02:03,790 --> 00:02:05,225
but at least he's sincere.

52
00:02:05,758 --> 00:02:07,327
The company's going to be in trouble.

53
00:02:08,628 --> 00:02:10,362
Why are you backing Bai Xing so hard?

54
00:02:10,363 --> 00:02:11,598
I'm not just backing him.

55
00:02:12,031 --> 00:02:13,766
I'm looking for a new market for you.

56
00:02:15,502 --> 00:02:16,835
Be honest with me.

57
00:02:16,836 --> 00:02:18,571
How was our performance today?

58
00:02:18,838 --> 00:02:20,673
Wasn't it better than you expected?

59
00:02:21,107 --> 00:02:22,407
Stop playing games.

60
00:02:22,408 --> 00:02:23,810
Let the talent speak for itself.

61
00:02:31,117 --> 00:02:32,118
Kids these days...

62
00:02:32,986 --> 00:02:34,954
They're definitely more
open-minded than us.

63
00:02:37,843 --> 00:02:39,083
I guess we'll just have to see.
